title: OT Genasis Interview and More
itunes:title: OT Genasis Interview and More
description:
Wednesday 11/8- Today on the show we had OT Genasis stop by for the first time, where he spoke about being signed to Busta Rhymes, new music and his love life that he tried to keep on the low, but the proof was right in front us during the interview. Moreover, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to Marilyn Manson because he aimed a fake rifle at a crowd. Also, Angela Yee helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee" with one listener who needed to be taught, to never doubt how crazy someone could be.
